		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="-Interact with Myrnath in TUT_Avernus_C 2; 21; -437&#xD;&#xA;-Manage to free Us from the skull, then attack him in dialogue&#xD;&#xA;-Let him reach the crevice in which he dissappears&#xD;&#xA;-He will teleport to 36; 18; -354 after a aprox 5 seconds then have him see you, being hostile and starting combat" />
